---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';

const webPageSchema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'WebPage',
  name: 'Terms of Service — CryptoCalk',
  description:
    'Terms of Service and legal disclaimer for using CryptoCalk calculators. We provide informational tools, not financial advice.',
  url: 'https://cryptocalk.com/terms/',
  inLanguage: 'en',
  dateModified: '2026-02-26T00:00:00+00:00',
};
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — CryptoCalk Usage Conditions"
  description="Terms of Service and legal disclaimer for using CryptoCalk calculators. We provide informational tools, not financial advice."
  lang="en"
>
  <SiteHeader lang="en" currentPath="/terms" />
  <main id="main-content" class="legal-container">
    <header class="legal-header">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p>Last updated: February 24, 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="legal-content">
      <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>Welcome to CryptoCalk ("we", "our", or "us"). By accessing or using our website (cryptocalk.com) and our calculators, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you disagree with any part of these terms, please do not use our website.</p>

      <h2>2. Not Financial Advice (Disclaimer)</h2>
      <p><strong>ALL CONTENT AND CALCULATOR OUTCOMES ON CRYPTOCALK ARE FOR INFORMATIONAL AND EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY.</strong></p>
      <p>We are not financial advisors, registered brokers, or tax professionals. The results provided by our calculators are estimates based on the inputs you provide and current market conditions. They do not constitute financial, investment, legal, or tax advice. You should not make any financial decisions based solely on the data provided by our tools.</p>
      <p>Cryptocurrency investments are highly volatile and risky. You are solely responsible for your own investment research and financial decisions. Always consult with a qualified professional before making any financial commitments.</p>

      <h2>3. Accuracy of Information</h2>
      <p>While we strive to provide accurate and up-to-date information, including real-time api price feeds, we make no warranties or representations regarding the accuracy, reliability, or completeness of any data or calculations. Prices, swap rates, network fees, and other variables fluctuate constantly. CryptoCalk assumes no liability for errors or omissions in the content or tools provided.</p>

      <h2>4. Use of the Service</h2>
      <p>You agree to use our calculators and tools responsibly. You must not:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the site for any illegal or unauthorized purpose.</li>
        <li>Attempt to scrape, extract, or mine data from the site automatically.</li>
        <li>Interfere with or disrupt the security or performance of the website.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Third-Party Links and APIs</h2>
      <p>Our website utilizes third-party APIs (such as CoinGecko) for live pricing data, and may contain links to third-party exchanges or services. We are not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party web sites or services. Accessing third-party links is at your own risk.</p>

      <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content, designs, calculator algorithms, and branding on CryptoCalk are the intellectual property of CryptoCalk and its creators, unless otherwise stated. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without our explicit permission.</p>

      <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>Under no circumstances shall CryptoCalk, its creators, or its affiliates be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages (including but not limited to loss of profits, data, or investment capital) arising out of or in connection with your use of our website or tools.</p>

      <h2>8. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify or replace these Terms at any time without prior notice. Your continued use of the website after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@cryptocalk.com">support@cryptocalk.com</a> or via our <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <SiteFooter lang="en" />
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(webPageSchema)} />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px;
  }
  .legal-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .legal-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .legal-header p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .legal-content {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .legal-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 40px 0 16px;
  }
  .legal-content p {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .legal-content ul {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    padding-left: 24px;
  }
  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .legal-content strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .legal-content a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .legal-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
